{"tid":2275571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉2.1億洗黑錢案　23歲男警獲准保釋候查","createTime":"2020-11-07T09:11:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T10:18:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d0d191e90761db8ce177e719608abc71fe70c3","tid":2275571,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:11:51.000Z","msg":"2020-11-07 14:26<br />\n<br />\n前日（5日）警方破獲一宗涉款達2.1億元的洗黑錢案，拘捕8男3女，他們涉嫌於去年3月至今年10月期間，處理總共2.1億元的懷疑犯罪得益。當中一名被捕人為23歲男警員，他隸屬新界南總區衝鋒隊，入職近4年，據知他嗜賭，經常赴濠江「搏殺」，欠下大筆賭債。至今日（7日）男警員已獲准保釋候查，須於12月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方毒品調查科財富調查組人員上月接獲線報，指懷疑多名人士的戶口有不尋常的大額金錢活動。經深入調查後，警方今日在全港多區拘捕8男3女，年齡介乎19至30歲，涉嫌處理已知道或相信為代表從可公訴罪行的得益的財產（俗稱洗黑錢）和串謀處理已知道或相信為代表從可公訴罪行的得益的財產。案情顯示，被捕人涉嫌於去年3月至今年10月期間，處理總共2.1億的懷疑犯罪得益，每個戶口交易金額約為500萬至7000萬。"},{"pid":"cc0fb2e66be1fa2c6aebc3f1dbe54c559704cf73","tid":2275571,"uid":323245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"見係狗就比保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529877e0caa49e0b8e34b0b9c65c0067dce52380","tid":2275571,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201107/IA7TOYZM3JE4NPOX777K3LUTTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201107%2FIA7TOYZM3JE4NPOX777K3LUTTQ%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=dd7c3ea9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201107%2FIA7TOYZM3JE4NPOX777K3LUTTQ%2F&h=d3dc77d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201107/IA7TOYZM3JE4NPOX777K3LUTTQ/</a>"},{"pid":"a7e9d45393f3de0a6ce5beeebe57768bc3c92c0c","tid":2275571,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:16:58.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1aeea24891f7f247528e7173fa226a106778ed","tid"